WEBVTT

00:10:59.024 --> 00:11:02.460
"She just went away
to find you water and food."

00:11:04.388 --> 00:11:06.381
But his heart soon stopped,

00:11:06.405 --> 00:11:10.078
and Doaa had to release
the little boy into the water.

00:11:11.023 --> 00:11:13.048
Later that day,

00:11:13.072 --> 00:11:16.351
she looked up into the sky with hope,

00:11:16.375 --> 00:11:20.390
because she saw two planes
crossing in the sky.

00:11:20.414 --> 00:11:24.913
And she waved her arms,
hoping they would see her,

00:11:24.937 --> 00:11:26.793
but the planes were soon gone.

00:11:27.317 --> 00:11:30.220
But that afternoon,
as the sun was going down,